data.description: NEW ROOF! It will be replaced the last week of Nov 2023.  Welcome to 2409 Antilles in beautiful Winter Park, where your dream home awaits! This immaculate property offers a perfect blend of modern upgrades and spacious living on almost. Step inside to discover a fully re-engineered and rebuilt 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home with an amazing chimney. The entire home has undergone a top-to-bottom renovation, leaving no stone unturned. All Doors, have been upgraded to ensure peace of mind and longevity. You can rest easy knowing you're essentially moving into a brand new home with a fresh start. As you step through the home, you'll appreciate the brand new Luxury Vinyl flooring and elegant  light fixtures. The living areas are spacious and perfect for entertaining or relaxing with loved ones.  Schedule your private showing today.
